ustainability and economic prosperity in the commonwealth  Symposium founder Captain Ronald A  Erchul  USN  Retired  was the coordinator of the conference until his retirement  Captain Erchul passed away in 2011    Previous Award Winners Governor s Environmental Excellence Awards  CAPT R A  Erchul  USN  Retired  Environmental Leadership Award  2015 Recipient   Jack Frye 2014 Recipient   Russ Baxter 2013 Recipient   Shelton Miles  2012 Recipients   E  Cabell Brand  and Timothy G  Hayes  Hunton   Williams  A full list of previous award winners is also available  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 